title: 'statement-store: Improve RPC Type Signatures'
doc:
- audience: Node Dev
  description: |-
    # Description

    Improves statement-store RPC API efficiency by replacing `[u8; 32]` array parameters with `Bytes` type

    ## Integration

    **Breaking Change**

    Binary parameters now serialize as hex strings (`"0x1a2b..."`) instead of numeric arrays (`[1, 2, 3, ...]`).
crates:
- name: sc-rpc-api
  bump: major
- name: sc-rpc
  bump: major
